name: Baby Luffy
description: Welcome to the exciting world of Baby uffy(BLF), where gaming meets crypto in a Click-To-Earn adventure! Get ready to embark on a thrilling journey that combines NFTs, treasure boxes, and exciting giveaways. In the world of Baby uffy, cards are your gateway to fortune and adventure. With four distinct rarities – Common, Rare, Epic, and Legendary – these cards hold the key to your success and the thrill of the unknown.
